## 6) docs/bytecode.md (header + sample opcodes)
```text
.kh bytecode quick reference


Header: 4 bytes magic ".kh!" (0x2E6B6821), u16 version_major, u16 version_minor


Sample opcodes:
0x01 LOAD_CONST <u32>
0x02 LOAD_LOCAL <u16>
0x03 STORE_LOCAL <u16>
0x04 ADD
0x05 SUB
0x06 MUL
0x07 DIV
0x0A CALL <u32> <u8>
0x0F RETURN


All integers little-endian. Section table and constant pool follow header.
